data.description: Home sweet home! This beautiful energy efficient home in Monticello Heights is awaiting a new family. This cozy home is already equipped with solar panels! As you approach this home you'll have a nice covered front porch for relaxing. Immediately as you walk through the front door, you'll notice that the living room and dining room has an open concept layout with tons of natural lighting. As you enter the kitchen, you'll have designer backsplash, plenty of countertop space, and a beautiful kitchen island. The living, dining and kitchen area have well-kept dark hardwood floors. There are 3 spacious size bedrooms and 1 updated full bath. This oversized backyard has a huge concrete slab perfect for barbequing and entertaining.
